resources.string: Āhei koe ki ara te pūrere e rua mirimiri i runga i te mata.

Āhei koe ki hono USB pūrere. A, no te whakahohe te tahi atu pūrere e pā ana USB mahi, taua rite ADB a MTP, e e kore kia wātea tae noa ki tenei ko monokia ranei te pūrere ko anō. e kore katoa USB pūrere e mahi.
piki te tūtohutanga o te pa ki mata na pa taea kia rēhita ia mau karapu.
Ka whakahohe i te tuarua sim kāri mokamoka. tenei kia e kore kia whakahohe te kore reira ko he sim kāri i roto i te tuarua mokamoka. (Me Anō!)

tenei mahi a tawhio noa take ki Snapchat, Instagram a te tahi atu ataata tuhi taupānga. whakamahinga te google avc encoder hei utu o te HW avc encoder. koe kia Me ki tīmata te taupānga ranei tīmata te pūrere i mua i tenei tautuhinga e pānga. tenei kia hoki take etahi ataata tuhi taupānga e kore ki mahi.
Kāore i tautoko e tenei pūrere...
Mauruuru koe katoa hoki koe tautoko!
